headline: Third-party delivery regulation issues continue in cities like New York and Seattle
summary: New York City recently eased delivery platform caps and DoorDash just raised prices in Seattle, calling it ‘the most expensive U.S. delivery market’

headline: Jenius Bank Named Title Sponsor for 2025 Pickleball World Championships
summary: DALLAS & LOS ANGELES, July 09, 2025--Jenius Bank partners with the Professional Pickleball Association and Major League Pickleball to continue promoting financial wellness for Americans.

headline: Elevating driver rewards: Lyft and Prezzee announce digital gift card partnership
summary: Lyft, one of North America's leading ride-hailing marketplaces, today announced a partnership with Prezzee, a global digital gifting company, to enhance the driver rewards experience with personalized, digital-first benefits.

headline: Oppenheimer Hikes DoorDash (DASH) Price Target on Earnings Growth Prospects
summary: DoorDash Inc. (NASDAQ:DASH) is one of the 12 best consumer goods stocks billionaires are quietly buying. On June 30, Oppenheimer reiterated an Outperform rating on the stock.
